action.prompt:
Please summarize the current page and help me create a Linear task reminder. Here's the page information:

**Page Title:** {pageTitle}
**URL:** {pageUrl}

**Main Content:**
{mainText}

Please:
1. Provide a brief summary of this page
2. Suggest a task title for Linear
3. Help me create a reminder task that captures the key information

What would you like the Linear task to be about?

action.code:
// Extract page information
const pageTitle = document.title;
const pageUrl = window.location.href;
const mainText = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('h1, h2, h3, p')).map(el => el.textContent).filter(text => text.trim()).slice(0, 10).join('\n');

// Create a summary object and store it
window.pageSummaryData = {
  title: pageTitle,
  url: pageUrl,
  content: mainText,
  timestamp: new Date().toISOString()
};

console.log('Page data captured:', window.pageSummaryData);

